类 BSTreeNode<E extends Comparable<? super E>>

java.lang.Object
implementations.BSTreeNode<E>
类型参数:
E - the type of element stored in the node, which must implement Comparable
所有已实现的接口:
Serializable
public class BSTreeNode<E extends Comparable<? super E>> extends Object implements Serializable
A class representing a node in a binary search tree (BST).

This class is generic and can hold elements of any type that implements the Comparable interface, allowing the elements to be compared for ordering. The node contains references to its left and right child nodes, forming the structure of the BST. The class also implements Serializable, enabling its instances to be serialized for persistence or transmission.
